{
  "stem": "5970.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 146,
      "text": "The first work, I remember, they brought us into a big, big, tremendous soccer hall.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 147,
      "text": "But it was outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 148,
      "text": "It only had a roof.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 149,
      "text": "It didn't have walls or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 150,
      "text": "And it was cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 151,
      "text": "And they told us to sort out millions of shoes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 152,
      "text": "There were piles of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 153,
      "text": "It was impossible to sort them out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 154,
      "text": "And while you were trying to do that, they screamed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 155,
      "text": "And they beat us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 156,
      "text": "And they shouted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 157,
      "text": "And it was an impossible task.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 158,
      "text": "We tried to do the best we could.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 159,
      "text": "So that was the first few days of our introduction to this first concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 160,
      "text": "And then I was chosen for another job.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 161,
      "text": "They had a basket weaving workshop there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 162,
      "text": "And we had to make baskets for the bombs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 163,
      "text": "They were like a cylinder.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 164,
      "text": "Each basket was the size of a bomb, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 165,
      "text": "It was a cylinder that big.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 166,
      "text": "And we had to weave these things with reeds.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 167,
      "text": "And the conditions were also terrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 168,
      "text": "And we were divided.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 169,
      "text": "The Germans divided everything into 100 and 10, in groups of tens and groups of hundreds like the ancient Romans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 170,
      "text": "And so I was in a group of 10.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 171,
      "text": "And we had to produce, each of us, eight baskets a day, which under normal circumstances, I suppose is not too bad.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 172,
      "text": "But in this freezing cold with the fingers not being so supple and the reeds had to be soaked in cold water, it was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 173,
      "text": "But we had to do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 174,
      "text": "Otherwise, there were punishments and all sorts of things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 175,
      "text": "And but I must say, we did help each other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 176,
      "text": "Now, the older people couldn't-- just couldn't do all that much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 177,
      "text": "So whatever extra we could do, we helped each other so that the quota should be done.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
